{"type": "article", "id": 8437, "title": "GolfJC 收纳架", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-14T07:45:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234921btaPWOmgyN8pcCsu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t还记得我们<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/8214.html\" target=\"_blank\">前几天推荐的自助剪发镜子</a>么，推出镜子 GolfJC 最近又推出了一款可以挂在墙上的“篮子”。篮子挂在墙上后，“底部”封闭，可以放置小物件，而篮子“上部” 镂空，可以选择悬挂物品。“篮子”有不同的尺寸和颜色可以选择，配合一个“井”字形状衣架，简洁而又实用。这是<a href=\"http://www.golfjc.com/GOLFJC/WORK.html\" target=\"_blank\"> GolfJC 的官方主页</a>，可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234917IoJY1O4GFVcNSZaQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234918KuysEnLgv0JHIG6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234918OTqgiusBkz32txAp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234919qvYIUFeSiPh51G6c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234919vb2ZhN8q4Goc0AzS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234920N5PqHI9BLQUfYFvC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234920v4rkUCLsx8zoF1Sf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}